{
  "stem": "6966.4",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And on another occasion, we march into the camp, and there were-- as I marched, I counted 12 gallows.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And I thought, they're frightening us, German propaganda.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "No, they weren't frightening us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "They meant it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And we stood there, and we're all being called-- 28,000 men in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And I was-- the short ones stood in the first row.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And then behind us, you get the next, and the behind them so the SS could always see your heads and count you.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I was standing in the front row.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was standing-- all my lot of the barrack were standing then very near to the gallows.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I said, look at the left.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In the distance, I can see men coming along.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then as they come near, I can count 12 men-- big men, fit, clean, white, blue-striped uniform, hair clipped, shaven, clean, and marching.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they pass [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] a few yards from me, pass me, and that's where the gallows were, twelve gallows.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Usually, there's three.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Three gallows are still there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But they had to make another 9.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It appears that two men had tried to run away and got in touch with civilian.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were caught.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And for reprisal, they took nine other men. 12 men were hung.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Well, they passed me by.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there were 12 little wooden boxes on the ground, and they had to stand on that.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Their hands were tied behind.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then the camp kapo-- that's the chief manager of the whole camp-- he put the, the noose around the neck and kicked away the box.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the body fell, and they were choked.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Number two saw what's happening to number one, then it was his turn.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Kicked away the thing, then they dropped.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
